<concept id="CMD_layerspanelclose">
   <title>LAYERSPANELCLOSE Command</title>
   <shortdesc>Closes the Layers Panel.</shortdesc>
   <conbody>
      <fig id="fig_okr_xxf_ynb">
         <image href="https://static.bricsys.com/help/en_US/V21/Common/command-reference-lite-pro-mechanical-bim.png" id="image_rsx_tpl_f4b" scope="external" />
      </fig>
      <p>Close the <xref keyref="PNL_layer" /> to hide it from the current workspace. If the Layers
         Panel is stacked when you close it, the Layers tab or icon is removed from the stack.</p>
   </conbody>
